GenAI has pushed the boundaries of what's possible and is poised to revolutionise the workplace and other aspects of society. The AI hype has driven inflated valuations, sparked government initiatives for regional AI hubs, and spurred significant investment in startups, all contributing to global economic growth. While businesses are eagerly exploring GenAI for competitive advantages, its potential to reshape society - for better or worse - is equally profound.
